22
00:02:43,610 --> 00:02:45,670
I just turned 16 this year.

23
00:02:47,390 --> 00:02:48,070
I'm 18.

24
00:02:48,230 --> 00:02:51,390
Your Highness, I heard that you used to study at Yiyang Academy.

25
00:02:51,560 --> 00:02:54,230
