33
00:03:12,190 --> 00:03:13,150
Did it scare you?

34
00:03:13,420 --> 00:03:14,220
No.

35
00:03:14,360 --> 00:03:15,730
I'm just not used to it.

36
00:03:18,390 --> 00:03:19,079
Guard Yu.

37
00:03:22,420 --> 00:03:23,960
