64
00:04:40,650 --> 00:04:41,560
To be honest,

65
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:44,680
I need your help.

66
00:04:48,510 --> 00:04:52,420
Although this may seem rude,

67
00:04:53,540 --> 00:04:54,990
