The cakes outside the city are very delicious.

98
00:06:45,700 --> 00:06:47,310
-Really? 
-I'll take you there next time.

99
00:06:58,710 --> 00:06:59,390
Zhu.

100
00:07:01,270 --> 00:07:01,870
Qinruo.

101
00:07:01,900 --> 00:07:03,980
